        {
            "title": "港股初段跌勢加劇 開市45分鐘左右已跌逾400點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今早初段跌勢明顯加劇，恒生指數在開市僅約45分鐘便跌逾400點，早前最低見22492點，挫451點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14719571-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%b7%8c%e5%8b%a2%e5%8a%a0%e5%8a%87-%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%8245%e5%88%86%e9%90%98%e5%b7%a6%e5%8f%b3%e5%b7%b2%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be400%e9%bb%9e",
